# 📊 Unemployment Analysis Dashboard  
## India Covid-19 Impact Analysis using Machine Learning

Transforming unemployment data into meaningful insights through Machine Learning, Analytics, and Interactive Visualization.

An interactive Data Science and Machine Learning project built using **Python**, **Streamlit**, and **Plotly** to analyze the impact of Covid-19 on unemployment trends across India.  

The dashboard provides powerful visual analytics, state-wise comparisons, rural vs urban analysis, and machine learning-based unemployment prediction.

---

# 🚀 Project Features

- 📈 Unemployment trend analysis over time
- 🗺️ State-wise unemployment comparison
- 🏙️ Urban vs Rural unemployment insights
- 📊 Interactive visualizations using Plotly
- 🔥 Correlation heatmap analysis
- 🤖 Machine Learning prediction model
- 🔮 Future unemployment rate prediction
- 📉 Statistical analysis and EDA
- 🎯 User-friendly interactive Streamlit dashboard

---

# 🧠 Technologies Used

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Plotly
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn

